"title": "4123: Satan, as deceiver",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4123: satan, as deceiver",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Satan's character is deceitful, devious and cunning as in a variety of guises he seeks to influence people for his own ends.</p>\n<h2>Satan's deceitful character</h2>\n<h3>He is evil</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:13\">MAT 6:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:37\">MAT 5:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:19\">MAT 13:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:15\">JHN 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:3\">2TH 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:13-1John2:14\">1JN 2:13–2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:8\">1JN 3:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:12\">1JN 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:18\">1JN 5:18</a></p>\n<h3>He is a liar</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:44\">JHN 8:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:4-Gen3:5\">GEN 3:4–3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:11\">JOB 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:5\">JOB 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:9\">REV 3:9</a></p>\n<h3>He is devious</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:14\">2CO 11:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:3\">2CO 11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:11\">EPH 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:9\">2TH 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:7\">1TI 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:26\">2TI 2:26</a></p>\n<h3>He is scheming</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:11\">EPH 6:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:10-2Cor2:11\">2CO 2:10–2:11</a></p>\n<h3>He is a slanderer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:9-Job1:11\">JOB 1:9–1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:14-1Tim5:15\">1TI 5:14–5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:9\">REV 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Satan's deceitful work</h2>\n<h3>He deceives individuals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:14\">1TI 2:14</a></strong> <em>Eve was deceived by Satan the serpent.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:25\">DAN 8:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:13\">2TI 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:9\">REV 12:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:3\">REV 20:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:10\">REV 20:10</a></p>\n<h3>He works counterfeit miracles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:9-2Thess2:10\">2TH 2:9–2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:11-Exod7:12\">EXO 7:11–7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:22\">EXO 7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:1-Deut13:2\">DEU 13:1–13:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:24\">MAT 24:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:22\">MRK 13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:13-Rev13:14\">REV 13:13–13:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:20\">REV 19:20</a></p>\n<h3>He appoints false prophets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:15\">MAT 7:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:5\">DEU 13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:26\">JER 23:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer28:15\">JER 28:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:21\">JER 29:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:6-Ezek13:10\">EZK 13:6–13:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1-2Pet2:3\">2PE 2:1–2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:18-2Pet2:19\">2PE 2:18–2:19</a></p>\n<h3>He misuses Scripture</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:6\">MAT 4:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:10\">LUK 4:10</a></p>\n<h3>He blinds unbelievers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a></strong></p>",
